@startuml
title Automation Framework - Module Call Flow: core

skinparam shadowing false
autonumber

actor "Any Consumer" as Consumer
participant "BoundingBox(...)" as BoundingBox
participant "OCRText(...)" as OCRText
participant "TextLocateSpec(...)" as TextLocate
participant "ObjectLocateSpec(...)" as ObjectLocate
participant "TestCase(...)" as TestCase
participant "FrameworkError /\nActionExecutionError /\nVerificationError" as Exceptions

Consumer -> BoundingBox : construct region value
Consumer -> OCRText : construct OCR entry
Consumer -> TextLocate : build text locate payload
Consumer -> ObjectLocate : build object locate payload
Consumer -> TestCase : assemble parsed case model

alt runtime failure
  Consumer -> Exceptions : raise shared framework exception
end

note over Consumer,Exceptions
  The core module is mostly passive.
  It provides shared models and exception types
  rather than orchestration-heavy call chains.
end note

@enduml
